          <h2>Anti-Corruption</h2>
          <p class="intro">
            Hana's commitment to operating with integrity and transparency, and our
            long-standing membership of Thailand's Private Sector Collective Action
            Coalition Against Corruption (CAC).
          </p>
        </header>

        <div class="statement">
          <div class="from">Statement from the Chairman &amp; CEO</div>
          <p>
            The Board of Directors recognises that good corporate governance,
            alongside environmental and social responsibility, is fundamental
            to sustainable growth for the benefit of all stakeholders. The company
            is committed to doing business with integrity and transparency through
            its anti-corruption policy.
          </p>
          <p>
            Hana has joined Thailand's Private Sector Collective Action Coalition
            Against Corruption (CAC) to counter corruption in any form. All directors,
            executives, and employees of the company strictly conform to the
            anti-corruption policy — and we expect the same of our stakeholders,
            in support of the UN Sustainable Development Goals.
          </p>
          <p class="attrib"><strong>Hana Microelectronics</strong> Board of Directors</p>
        </div>

